    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.sin(v0 + 0.05) - (v2 + 0.42 + v0 + 0.55)))
    v1 = wp.exp((v1 / (v2 + 0.83 - v2 + 0.10)))
    tmp = 0.28
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.70)) + wp.sin(wp.cos(tmp + 0.22)))
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = 0.78
    v2 = wp.abs((wp.abs(v2 + 0.00) - 0.82))
    data[tid] = v0
